Policy
├── id (UUID)
├── organization_id (FK)
├── title
├── description
├── content (rich text)
├── category
├── version_number
├── status (draft, under_review, approved, published, retired)
├── owner_id (FK - User)
├── approver_id (FK - User)
├── approved_at
├── published_at
├── review_frequency (days)
├── next_review_date
├── parent_version_id (FK - self-referencing)
├── tags (array)
├── created_by (FK - User)
├── created_at
└── updated_at